Napoli-Daboli or whatever.

04:13.486 --> 04:16.421
Neapolitan. But this
is about Italy as a whole.

04:17.757 --> 04:21.692
Did the squirrels eat the bread I put out
for the ducks, or somebody sweep it up?

04:21.761 --> 04:25.128
