- Make a go of it at that new school.

04:39.912 --> 04:42.244
You got no idea
what we did to get you in there.

04:42.315 --> 04:45.443
There is no reason you shouldn't
be able to pass Social Studies.

04:45.518 --> 04:47.418
You passing Social Studies?

04:47.820 --> 04:50.050
