why I want you with me this week?

06:01.994 --> 06:04.394
God forbid you'd explain.
- That's right.

06:04.464 --> 06:08.525
Now you're gonna get fresh about it?
- I'm just saying, I mean, I'm glad to do it.

06:08.601 --> 06:10.398
I'm glad you're glad.

06:18.578 --> 06:20.603
You know, your father was
like a mentor to me.

06:20.680 --> 06:22.477
Right.
- A standup.

06:22.949 --> 06:25.782
You ask anybody.
Your old man was a legend.

06:26.285 --> 06:29.345
He single-handedly hunted down
that New England crew.

06:29.522 --> 06:32.150
Brought the war home to them up there.

06:34.761 --> 06:36.251
Another Chevy.

06:40.700 --> 06:41.792
Nuns.

06:42.602 --> 06:45.162
Might be undercover Feds, but I doubt it.

06:57.784 --> 06:59.513
He must be colicky.

07:03.823 --> 07:06.417
I think he likes your hair better that way.

07:13.933 --> 07:15.491
Mr. Soprano.

07:16.169 --> 07:17.397
There she is.

07:17.470 --> 07:20.769
You be good now, don't start.
- You ought to see my finish.

07:22.508 --> 07:24.874
You get sued for talk like that nowadays.

07:24.944 --> 07:27.378
