Let me die now.

07:27.447 --> 07:29.415
If a man can't voice to a beautiful woman...

07:29.482 --> 07:31.575
the zephyrs that are blowing
through his mind-

07:31.651 --> 07:33.209
God, listen to him today.

07:33.286 --> 07:36.050
Go in there now,
and strip down to your shorts.

07:36.956 --> 07:40.653
