10:27.426 --> 10:30.054
You wanna say hello to Danielle?
- Not really.

10:30.529 --> 10:33.259
I should go, anyhow.
- Enjoy your wine.

10:33.733 --> 10:37.169
Don't listen to his bullshit.
- I got to get up early tomorrow.

10:37.236 --> 10:40.137
No matter how much the john offers you?
- Pig.

10:42.575 --> 10:44.236
This is beautiful.

10:45.778 --> 10:48.975
Where'd you get it?
- You said you were gonna go. Go.

10:49.482 --> 10:51.916
I got to get some sleep.
- I should go.

10:55.988 --> 10:59.719
Froze to death in that mall today.
They go crazy with the air-conditioning.

11:00.192 --> 11:03.161
So, when am I gonna see you again?
