11:03.496 --> 11:04.758
Okay, sweetie.

11:07.166 --> 11:08.997
Some of those bags look like Gucci.

11:09.068 --> 11:12.231
Yeah, he gets that stuff all the time.
His cousin's a liquidator.

11:12.304 --> 11:13.771
Bye.
- See you.

11:17.109 --> 11:20.636
