12:13.265 --> 12:16.325
When the fuck have
I ever not been there 100 percent?

13:13.526 --> 13:14.857
Want some?

13:16.028 --> 13:17.859
Can I talk to you a minute?

13:23.502 --> 13:24.833
Turn this off?

13:25.805 --> 13:27.238
Turn it down.

13:33.145 --> 13:34.772
I'm worried, Tony.

13:34.847 --> 13:37.145
About my weight?
