than usual. I told you, it's temporary.

13:41.320 --> 13:43.584
Super Bowl last year,
we didn't lay enough off.

13:43.656 --> 13:45.146
No, it's not just that.

13:45.224 --> 13:47.624
I'm worried about you, about the future...

13:47.693 --> 13:50.059
