lots of people set up trusts for their kids...

15:06.038 --> 15:09.132
begin asset allocation-
- I got to spell this out for you?

15:09.208 --> 15:11.733
I can't declare X amount of my income.

15:11.810 --> 15:14.540
Your consulting fees
from Barone Sanitation you do.

15:14.613 --> 15:17.605
