15:36.368 --> 15:38.393
or wherever you put it at zero growth.

15:38.470 --> 15:40.938
The money stays put.
With what's going on globally...

15:41.006 --> 15:43.839
There's always some excuse.
- There's no cash in this house.

15:43.909 --> 15:45.843
Not since our last bust.

15:45.911 --> 15:47.344
Check the vents.

15:48.747 --> 15:51.682
And I provide for my children.
- Yes, Tony, you do.

15:52.051 --> 15:54.713
But I don't know how you do it,
because you won't tell me.

15:54.787 --> 15:57.950
Let me tell you something,
or you can watch the fucking news:

15:58.023 --> 15:59.718
Everything comes to an end.

16:10.402 --> 16:11.892
Good morning, Ton'.

16:13.739 --> 16:16.833
They over there?
