16:18.143 --> 16:19.770
What the fuck are you doing?

16:19.845 --> 16:22.541
What?
- You're wasting fucking ice.

16:22.648 --> 16:25.481
It's mostly melted.
- You're fucking arguing with me now?

16:25.551 --> 16:26.540
No, Ton'.

16:26.618 --> 16:30.213
