- No.

16:40.265 --> 16:43.098
I think you are.
You're getting a fucking attitude on you.

16:43.168 --> 16:44.362
I'm not.

16:48.474 --> 16:51.875
Ice, when it hangs around-
- Georgie, be quiet.

16:52.811 --> 16:55.575
