16:55.647 --> 16:58.047
especially Scotch.
- Jesus Christ.

16:59.018 --> 17:00.508
Here, throw it all away.

17:00.586 --> 17:03.555
Waste it all, fucking John D. Rockefeller!
Waste it all!

17:10.561 --> 17:11.824
Conserve.

17:28.614 --> 17:30.138
Where were you?

17:38.724 --> 17:42.387
