on the street, crack some heads.

17:55.607 --> 17:57.837
Create some fucking earners out there.

18:03.482 --> 18:04.710
The guy...

18:04.783 --> 18:08.241
We talked about this,
over at the other place with the guy.

18:08.520 --> 18:11.421
