46:11.101 --> 46:13.092
Karen. Did something happen?

46:13.437 --> 46:15.769
We got some bad news last night.

46:17.007 --> 46:19.066
Are you just gonna stand there?

46:19.143 --> 46:23.102
The Feds had an undercover agent
in Dr. Schreck's office.

46:30.354 --> 46:31.787
Uncle Jun'.

46:32.122 --> 46:34.955
Hey, Karen.
- Fucking Grand Central Station?

46:35.025 --> 46:36.754
Junior, my kids?

46:37.594 --> 46:39.721
You're right. Sorry, dear.

46:39.797 --> 46:41.765
I brought my bar of soap.

46:41.865 --> 46:43.662
What time they call you?

46:43.734 --> 46:47.500
We had a little scare.
Thought it was the shunt in his heart.

46:47.571 --> 46:50.233
He passed some gas, and he seems better.

46:50.307 --> 46:53.902
Why don't you go on Joe Franklin,
tell the whole tri-state area?

46:55.345 --> 46:56.334
Dad.

46:57.915 --> 46:59.177
Not now.

46:59.249 --> 47:01.046
I heard what happened.

47:01.118 --> 47:04.417
It's bad, but it's not worth
getting yourself sick over.

47:05.088 --> 47:07.921
I told you, just sit down.
- He doesn't have cable.

47:10.194 --> 47:11.718
Actually, we're gonna go.

47:11.795 --> 47:14.161
Okay, Jun', you got everything?

47:14.598 --> 47:17.089
Thank you, dear, you've been wonderful.

47:17.167 --> 47:18.464
Bye, Karen.

47:18.535 --> 47:20.662
I'll see you. See you, kids.

47:20.838 --> 47:22.396
Goodbye, Karen.
- Be good.

47:25.042 --> 47:27.374
Must've been that piece of tail.

47:33.517 --> 47:35.212
Now, look, she...

47:36.687 --> 47:38.678
She probably reported the meetings...

47:38.755 --> 47:40.985
who was there, all that shit.

47:42.759 --> 47:44.818
As far as conversations,
what could she hear?

47:44.895 --> 47:46.556
You'd better hope nothing...

47:46.630 --> 47:49.690
because you were involved
in every fucking one.

47:52.870 --> 47:56.499
How could you fall for that flirty shit?
That's the point!

47:59.776 --> 48:03.007
Get the hell outta here.
I wanna talk to my uncle.

48:07.517 --> 48:11.681
Forget about that for a minute.
That shit about your legal expenses.

48:12.923 --> 48:15.483
I been thinking, and okay.

48:17.094 --> 48:19.528
Maybe I can give you some relief.

48:19.897 --> 48:20.989
What?

48:22.332 --> 48:25.563
You got that empty garage
over on Frelinghuysen Avenue.

48:25.636 --> 48:28.332
You been trying to sell it.
I'll take it off your hands.

48:28.405 --> 48:32.398
What are you gonna do with it?
- I don't know, I'm trying to help you out.

48:32.643 --> 48:33.871
How much?

48:35.612 --> 48:36.909
$100,000.

48:39.950 --> 48:41.474
Who gives a fuck anyway?

48:41.551 --> 48:44.349
Come on.
- I was led around by the nose, Anthony.

48:44.421 --> 48:48.653
You're right. A young cooze smiled at me,
and birds started chirping.

48:49.126 --> 48:52.618
Time was, my instincts would've never
failed me like that.

48:52.696 --> 48:54.994
So, what are you now, the Amazing Kreskin?

48:55.065 --> 48:56.828
What did I tell her?

48:56.900 --> 48:59.266
Did I say anything
could be used against me?

48:59.336 --> 49:00.735
I don't know.

49:00.804 --> 49:02.999
Bullshitting, singing.

49:03.240 --> 49:05.367
Atlantic City, Jesus Christ.

49:06.677 --> 49:10.135
I'll be sitting right across from her
in the courtroom.

49:18.088 --> 49:20.750
All right, come on. Have something to eat.

49:24.461 --> 49:26.429
I'm an old man, Anthony.

49:28.065 --> 49:30.465
An old man that's going to trial.

49:32.202 --> 49:34.170
Not much else to say about me.

49:53.590 --> 49:55.217
I'm a little depressed.

49:57.894 --> 49:59.293
You were on vacation.

49:59.363 --> 50:01.593
Can you describe the feelings?

50:01.932 --> 50:03.524
Things are good.

50:05.369 --> 50:07.337
Especially with Carmela.

50:09.106 --> 50:11.939
But then she starts ragging on me
about the future.

50:12.009 --> 50:13.670
How she's worried.

50:14.344 --> 50:16.574
And what's gonna happen to them
if I'm dead.

50:16.646 --> 50:19.012
And 'buy bonds' and all this shit.

50:19.182 --> 50:21.707
A lot of people are feeling vulnerable.

50:21.785 --> 50:24.276
On the other hand, she's right.

50:25.055 --> 50:27.956
Not that I'd ever tell her that.
- Why not?

50:28.925 --> 50:31.723
'Cause then she'd wanna know
where's the money, how much.

50:31.795 --> 50:34.093
Don't you want Carmela to be taken care of?

50:34.164 --> 50:35.324
She is.

50:35.932 --> 50:37.797
Anyway, she's right, that's the point.

50:37.868 --> 50:40.598
Over the last few years,
I've been doing a lot of thinking.

50:40.670 --> 50:41.659
And?

50:41.872 --> 50:44.306
My uncle definitely snapped it into focus.

50:44.374 --> 50:47.036
What's he, 72 years old? What's he got?

50:47.110 --> 50:50.375
Fucking shitty house in Belleville,
and a bunch of legal bills...

50:50.447 --> 50:53.348
that'd make you gargle Drano
if you had them.

50:53.550 --> 50:55.177
I've analyzed it.

50:56.686 --> 50:58.881
There's two endings for a guy like me.

50:58.955 --> 51:00.582
High-profile guy.

51:01.124 --> 51:02.921
Dead, or in the can.

51:03.126 --> 51:05.959
Big percent of the time.
- You've never talked this frankly.

51:06.029 --> 51:09.624
Even with all this terrorism shit,
the government has resources up the ass.

51:09.699 --> 51:12.065
As far as legal bills are-
- Anthony!

51:12.135 --> 51:14.194
What?
- Why don't you give it up?

51:17.174 --> 51:19.199
You didn't let me finish.

51:19.443 --> 51:21.877
There's a third way to wrap it up.

51:22.913 --> 51:24.881
You rely only on family.

51:25.082 --> 51:29.018
Not many men could survive
without the love and support...

51:29.086 --> 51:31.179
of their wife and children.

51:31.254 --> 51:33.484
No, I'm talking about business.

51:33.557 --> 51:35.388
You trust only blood.

51:39.396 --> 51:41.125
A friend of mine...

51:41.231 --> 51:43.324
guy whose name you wouldn't know...

51:43.400 --> 51:45.265
stayed out of the can and in charge.

51:45.335 --> 51:49.601
Lived in Florida till he was 81 years old.
He only gave orders through his son.

51:51.441 --> 51:55.002
No other conversations
that could come back in testimony.

51:55.946 --> 51:57.880
His son?
- No, not A.J.

51:59.282 --> 52:01.716
What I've been dealt is my nephew.

52:02.919 --> 52:05.513
He's gotten his act together, the kid.

52:07.357 --> 52:08.824
Over the last few months...

52:08.892 --> 52:12.384
I started the process
of bonding him to me inseparably.

52:13.096 --> 52:14.085
How?

52:14.631 --> 52:16.292
That we can't get into.

52:16.366 --> 52:18.300
Didn't your uncle do that with you?

52:18.368 --> 52:22.134
You said his life is like a desert.

52:22.205 --> 52:25.299
I'm 42, and I'm already more successfuI
than my uncle ever was.

52:25.375 --> 52:27.036
You've seen my house.

52:29.746 --> 52:32.374
Anthony, why are you telling me this?

52:39.656 --> 52:41.123
I don't know.

52:42.559 --> 52:45.392
Guess I trust you.

52:47.898 --> 52:49.195
A little.

53:16.593 --> 53:17.855
Hi, Mom.

53:19.629 --> 53:22.860
What the hell are you doing here?
You scared me to death.

53:22.933 --> 53:25.527
Just stopped by
to see how you're getting along.

53:25.602 --> 53:29.299
You ever do anything like a normal person?
There is a bell.

53:31.841 --> 53:33.308
How you been?

53:33.743 --> 53:34.835
Fine.

53:36.780 --> 53:38.407
How's Connie's kid?

53:38.481 --> 53:39.812
He's huge.

53:40.850 --> 53:42.044
Jesus!

53:43.753 --> 53:45.220
That's Jason?

53:46.690 --> 53:49.853
He has a weight problem already.
Eight years old.

53:49.926 --> 53:53.418
She never had him baptized.
She thought she knew everything.

53:53.496 --> 53:57.660
Actually, I was hoping you would make me
one of your fluffernutters.

54:01.871 --> 54:03.771
It's fucking mouthwash.

54:03.940 --> 54:07.637
Leave me the fuck alone.
You come over here with that shit.

54:13.783 --> 54:16.877
What's that on the table,
Daddy's navy picture?

54:17.554 --> 54:19.283
You ever miss him?

54:21.157 --> 54:23.022
When he was in prison...

54:23.393 --> 54:25.361
or since he's been dead?

54:27.297 --> 54:28.764
I don't know.

54:33.637 --> 54:36.128
Did I saddle you with a stepfather?

54:48.351 --> 54:52.219
I don't have any peanut butter.
I haven't kept it since you left.

54:52.289 --> 54:54.689
I can't make you a fluffernutter.

54:55.225 --> 54:57.125
You want French toast?

54:59.696 --> 55:01.061
I gotta go.

55:05.602 --> 55:08.594
Ade sends her love.
- Right, say hello.

55:11.041 --> 55:14.067
You watch that Bailey's,
or I'll give you a shot in the head.

55:14.144 --> 55:15.873
Look who's talking.
- What?

55:15.945 --> 55:17.537
Never mind what.

